<ab facs="#facs_184_r1l15">danyden geſtallt ıſt / . vnd ob Jr die <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
