<ab facs="#facs_184_r1l19"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> / So laſſet es <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd ob Jr die brıef <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r1l20"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht / wär es / daʒ es an ıhte hafftet / wie es <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r1l21"><expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeÿ / das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbt</expan> vns eigentlıch / vnd was ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r1l23">auch güt dewcht daʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_184_r1l22">fürbas </ab></add> dar cʒü cʒetun <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>Sup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
